    1

    BMI :

    BMI Range BMI Category
    Less than 18.5 Underweight
    18.5 24.9 Normal weight
    25 and above Obesity 
    df_smoking["BMI"] = df_smoking["weight(kg)"] / ((df_smoking["height(cm)"] / 100) ** 2)

correlation = df_smoking['BMI'].corr(df_smoking['systolic'])
print('The correlation between study load and sleep quality:', correlation)

    The correlation between study load and sleep quality: 0.3038276850047082

    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 3))
plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
sns.regplot(x='BMI', y='systolic', data=df_smoking, scatter=False, line_kws={"color":"red"})
plt.title('r = 0.303827685004708')
plt.grid(True)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

    conditions_BMI = [df_smoking['BMI'] < 18.5, (df_smoking['BMI'] >= 18.5) & (df_smoking['BMI'] < 25),(df_smoking['BMI'] >= 25)]

labels_BMI = ['Underweight', 'Normal', 'Obese']
df_smoking['BMI Category'] = np.select(conditions_BMI, labels_BMI)

df_smoking['smoking'] = df_smoking['smoking'].map({1: 'Smoker', 0: 'Non-Smoker'})

plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
sns.boxplot(data=df_smoking, x='BMI Category', y='systolic', hue='smoking',
    palette={'Non-Smoker': "#D9D9D9", 'Smoker': "#C4BBA7"})

plt.ylim(40, 180)
plt.title('Systolic Blood Pressure by BMI Category and Smoking Status', fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel('BMI Category')
plt.ylabel('Systolic Blood Pressure')
plt.legend(title='Smoking Status')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

    :

    Systolic BP Range (mmHg) Systolic Category
    120 or below Normal
    Above 120 Abnormal (High) 
    systolic_threshold = 120 
df_smoking['Systolic Category'] = 'Abnormal'
df_smoking.loc[df_smoking['systolic'] <= systolic_threshold, 'Systolic Category'] = 'Normal'

df_smoking['Smoking Status'] = df_smoking['smoking'].map({0: 'Non-Smoker', 1: 'Smoker'})

palette_updated = { 'Non-Smoker': "#D9D9D9",  'Smoker': "#C4BBA7"}

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
sns.barplot( data=df_smoking, x='Systolic Category',  y='Gtp',   hue='smoking',   palette=palette_updated)
plt.title('GTP Levels by Systolic Blood Pressure Category and Smoking Status', fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel('Systolic Blood Pressure Category', fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('Average GTP Level', fontsize=12)
plt.legend(title='Smoking (1 = Yes, 0 = No)')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

    r_by_group = pd.DataFrame({
    'Age Group': ['Young (2030)', 'Young (2030)', 'Middle (3150)', 'Middle (3150)',
                  'Old (5165)', 'Old (5165)', 'Old Plus (6685)', 'Old Plus (6685)'],
    'Smoking Status': ['Non-Smoker', 'Smoker'] * 4,
    'Correlation (r)': [-0.405, -0.375, -0.427, -0.380, -0.386, -0.314, -0.356, -0.288]
})

#
